Move initialization code for gdev fields before it is added to
gpio_devices, with adjacent initialization code.
Adjust goto statements  to reflect modified order of operations

Backporting notes: moved code differs from upstream. This will have
to be revisited if we ever backport fcc8b637c542 ("gpiolib: switch the
line state notifier to atomic") and dcb73cbaaeb3 ("gpio: cdev: use raw
notifier for line state events").

